trans-unit.source: Represents a token that represents a string.
trans-unit.target: Representa um token que representa uma cadeia de caracteres.

trans-unit.source: Indicates whether the current instance is equal to a specified object.
trans-unit.target: Indica se a instância atual é igual ao objeto especificado.

trans-unit.source: The object to compare with this <see langword="StringToken" />.
trans-unit.target: O objeto a ser comparado com este <see langword="StringToken" />.

trans-unit.source: Checks if the given object is an instance of <see langword="StringToken" /> and is equal to this instance.
trans-unit.target: Verifica se o objeto fornecido é uma instância de <see langword="StringToken" /> e é igual a esta instância.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if <paramref name="obj" /> is an instance of <see langword="StringToken" /> and is equal to this object; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> se <paramref name="obj" /> for uma instância de <see langword="StringToken" /> e for igual a este objeto; caso contrário, <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Reflection.Emit.StringToken" /> to compare to the current instance.
trans-unit.target: O <see cref="T:System.Reflection.Emit.StringToken" /> a ser comparado com a instância atual.

trans-unit.source: Indicates whether the current instance is equal to the specified <see cref="T:System.Reflection.Emit.StringToken" />.
trans-unit.target: Indica se a instância atual é igual ao <see cref="T:System.Reflection.Emit.StringToken" /> especificado.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the value of <paramref name="obj" /> is equal to the value of the current instance; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> se o valor de <paramref name="obj" /> for igual ao valor da instância atual; caso contrário, <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: Returns the hash code for this string.
trans-unit.target: Retorna o código hash desta cadeia de caracteres.

trans-unit.source: Returns the underlying string token.
trans-unit.target: Retorna o token de cadeia de caracteres subjacente.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Reflection.Emit.StringToken" /> to compare to <c>b</c>.
trans-unit.target: O <see cref="T:System.Reflection.Emit.StringToken" /> a ser comparado com <c>b</c>.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Reflection.Emit.StringToken" /> to compare to <c>a</c>.
trans-unit.target: O <see cref="T:System.Reflection.Emit.StringToken" /> a ser comparado com <c>a</c>.

trans-unit.source: Indicates whether two <see cref="T:System.Reflection.Emit.StringToken" /> structures are equal.
trans-unit.target: Indica se duas estruturas <see cref="T:System.Reflection.Emit.StringToken" /> são iguais.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if <paramref name="a" /> is equal to <paramref name="b" />; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> se <paramref name="a" /> for igual a <paramref name="b" />; caso contrário, <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: The equivalent method for this operator is <xref:System.Reflection.Emit.StringToken.Equals%28System.Reflection.Emit.StringToken%29?displayProperty=nameWithType>.
trans-unit.target: O método equivalente para esse operador é <xref:System.Reflection.Emit.StringToken.Equals%28System.Reflection.Emit.StringToken%29?displayProperty=nameWithType>.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Reflection.Emit.StringToken" /> to compare to <c>b</c>.
trans-unit.target: O <see cref="T:System.Reflection.Emit.StringToken" /> a ser comparado com <c>b</c>.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Reflection.Emit.StringToken" /> to compare to <c>a</c>.
trans-unit.target: O <see cref="T:System.Reflection.Emit.StringToken" /> a ser comparado com <c>a</c>.

trans-unit.source: Indicates whether two <see cref="T:System.Reflection.Emit.StringToken" /> structures are not equal.
trans-unit.target: Indica se duas estruturas <see cref="T:System.Reflection.Emit.StringToken" /> não são iguais.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if <paramref name="a" /> is not equal to <paramref name="b" />; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> se <paramref name="a" /> não for igual a <paramref name="b" />; caso contrário, <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: The equivalent method for this operator is <xref:System.Reflection.Emit.StringToken.Equals%28System.Reflection.Emit.StringToken%29?displayProperty=nameWithType>.
trans-unit.target: O método equivalente para esse operador é <xref:System.Reflection.Emit.StringToken.Equals%28System.Reflection.Emit.StringToken%29?displayProperty=nameWithType>.

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the metadata token for this string.
trans-unit.target: Recupera o token de metadados dessa cadeia de caracteres.

trans-unit.source: Read-only.
trans-unit.target: Somente leitura.

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the metadata token of this string.
trans-unit.target: Recupera o token de metadados da cadeia de caracteres.
